description: This is a JavaScript source file serving as the entry point for a React web application. It initializes the React application by rendering the main App component inside the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components, targeting the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React application wrapped in StrictMode inside the created root.
